{"tid":413293,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"【大件事】DSE嘅入一入黎","createTime":"2017-09-25T10:55:25.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T22:31:28.000Z","uid":20848,"like":8,"dislike":42,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"7c3710c105ceaf62133ac8e6719266cdc58d3af7","tid":413293,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:55:25.000Z","msg":"算唔算廣告我唔知，因為我做緊嘅野係零profit，亦都唔係sell你地咩，但係你留低負皮之前，都睇下我係賣咩先。<br />\n<br />\n簡單黎講，我同一班大學朋友整左個<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">WhatsApp DSE Newsletter</span></span></strong></div><br />\n<br />\n比DSE嘅同學去訂閱。訂閱左嘅同學會<ins>定期透過WhatsApp收到一個mesaage</ins>，當中會有唔同有關DSE嘅資訊，暫時會包括以下幾大範疇：<br />\n<br />\n- <strong>最新學習資源</strong>（如past/mock paper，唔洗你比錢買同周圍揾）<br />\n- <strong>免費網上課程</strong>（唔好期望學到咩考試神技，我地唔係所謂「名師」，主要會教concept，而家會focus係數學科）<br />\n- <strong>讀書心得</strong>（只係由唔同人分享一下佢地對讀書嘅心得或者一D讀書嘅方法，已經寫左好幾篇，有興趣嘅可以去下面條link睇下）<br />\n<br />\n有興趣嘅用下面條link就可以免費訂閱，大家有咩想知想問都歡迎一齊討論下。另外如果有巴絲打有興趣寫D野，咩都好啦，總之你覺得岩中學生睇嘅都可以tg我傾下。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>已完成文章</strong><br />\n<a href=\"http://afterschoolcommunity.com/寫筆記的正確方法/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fafterschoolcommunity.com%2F%E5%AF%AB%E7%AD%86%E8%A8%98%E7%9A%84%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95%2F&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9bd6891e\" target=\"_blank\">http://afterschoolcommunity.com/寫筆記的正確方法/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://afterschoolcommunity.com/後設認知-十分鐘就有效提升成績？/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fafterschoolcommunity.com%2F%E5%BE%8C%E8%A8%AD%E8%AA%8D%E7%9F%A5-%E5%8D%81%E5%88%86%E9%90%98%E5%B0%B1%E6%9C%89%E6%95%88%E6%8F%90%E5%8D%87%E6%88%90%E7%B8%BE%EF%BC%9F%2F&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5e8f4199\" target=\"_blank\">http://afterschoolcommunity.com/後設認知-十分鐘就有效提升成績？/</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://afterschoolcommunity.com/2017-dse生-讀書心得分享（一）/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fafterschoolcommunity.com%2F2017-dse%E7%94%9F-%E8%AE%80%E6%9B%B8%E5%BF%83%E5%BE%97%E5%88%86%E4%BA%AB%EF%BC%88%E4%B8%80%EF%BC%89%2F&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=c067ebd5\" target=\"_blank\">http://afterschoolcommunity.com/2017-dse生-讀書心得分享（一）/</a><br />\n<br />\n訂閱連結：<a href=\"https://goo.gl/TvgZ3e\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgoo.gl%2FTvgZ3e&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=5bd9372c\" target=\"_blank\">https://goo.gl/TvgZ3e</a><br />\nInstagram: <a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/afterschool_hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fafterschool_hk&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=b2e8ad1f\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/afterschool_hk</a><br />\nBlog: <a href=\"http://www.afterschoolcommunity.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.afterschoolcommunity.com&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=36753df2\" target=\"_blank\">www.afterschoolcommunity.com</a><br />\n聯絡我們: <a href=\"https://t.me/AfterSchool_HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FAfterSchool_HK&d=EmZZZCWKfEHwDLUbmB0FXWi1w7%2FDyS2Kz%2BsYtkalU0Y%3D&h=9d8b8516\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/AfterSchool_HK</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3001176c990d8ac92aa6cd067d4911a7831e3cf4","tid":413293,"uid":71508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:58:33.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"8ea097bd25d99582b97a053fd5d3195f77fe4843","tid":413293,"uid":137768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10:58:54.000Z","msg":"寫左好多年筆記都係9寫 自己睇翻去煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd90d590cf37a7424c8ec2fb5b197d4266ddb95f","tid":413293,"uid":137768,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T10