6955c1454d7b304bd12","tid":413293,"uid":2679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:03:55.000Z","msg":"Repeater留名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e961fa266f7ce507045e926da67860eb2f44472","tid":413293,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:07:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>用telegram會唔會好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點解咁講？但學生應該未必個個都有用？</blockquote><br />\n純粹覺得telegram唔洗留電話 方便啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nOk la我諗學生都係用Whatsapp 多！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d8bfab30f860f897dd1a16cc87dfc043f5b0e36","tid":413293,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:08:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寫左好多年筆記都係9寫 自己睇翻<span style=\"color: red;\">好</span>煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote></blockquote><br />\n咩野自己睇翻好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己jot嘅notes 隨意寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果自己都D NOTES都睇唔明-&gt;你啲notes唔夠系統性-&gt;你學習都係好無系統性<br />\n呢點應該可以改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整理左自己既知識先寫落notes可以幫到你抄一次又整理一次 <br />\n記野會易記過死背好多</blockquote><br />\n我自己就慣性上堂抄notes會好亂，但係逼自己係同一日花時間整理翻D notes，咁就好好多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5469a0307d5d9749bf4e209bc4bf83e7bf5e2c","tid":413293,"uid":20848,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T14:09:52.000Z","msg":"唔明留負皮嘅人咩心態<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有咩做得唔好講啊麻，咁樣真係好咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.g