bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n自己jot嘅notes 隨意寫<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n如果自己都D NOTES都睇唔明-&gt;你啲notes唔夠系統性-&gt;你學習都係好無系統性<br />\n呢點應該可以改善下<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n整理左自己既知識先寫落notes可以幫到你抄一次又整理一次 <br />\n記野會易記過死背好多</blockquote><br />\n的確係 我學野好多東一忽西一忽<br />\n只係記得啲concepts<br />\n如果有人問起我我多數第一下答唔到關鍵嘅位<br />\n要講下講下先講到main point<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有無人同我一樣"},{"pid":"13bab0d446a1dfa12b2087bb0cf8e650407de228","tid":413293,"uid":20848,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T00:21:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我淨係想要啲past paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有做整合，因為知好多時候同學要花好多時間揾黎揾去又未必齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c321eac86961345f5fd2c7480818ddcfe49359d","tid":413293,"uid":123907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T01:45:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我淨係想要啲past paper<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我都有做整合，因為知好多時候同學要花好多時間揾黎揾去又未必齊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有無pp 大佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nDSE個啲好難揾"}]}